dcterms:creator: Sumanth V Rao
dcterms:description: This dataset consists of 1462 data points with 4 daily features: mean temperature, humidity, wind speed, and mean pressure. These features were experimentally measured in Delhi, India for weather forecasting.
dcterms:title: Daily Climate time-series Data (DC)

dcterms:creator: Matteo De Felice
dcterms:description: This dataset consists of weekly hydrological data from 27 European countries spanning the period 2015 to 2019, totalling 208 data points. The dataset includes hydropower inflows and average river discharges measured at national hydropower plants.
dcterms:title: Hydropower modelling with hydrological data (HM)

dcterms:creator: szrlee
dcterms:description: The dataset consists of 3019 data points and includes 6 daily features: the stock’s price at open and close, the highest and lowest price, the number of shares traded, and the stock’s ticker name. The data was collected for 29 DJIA companies.
dcterms:title: DJIA 30 Stock time series (DJIA)
